WEBVTT

00:18.280 --> 00:25.040
[2012]

01:00.380 --> 01:01.290
Jin...

01:07.560 --> 01:08.480
Stop packing.

01:08.789 --> 01:09.789
I'll do it for you.

01:10.150 --> 01:11.070
Okay.

01:41.350 --> 01:42.280
Are you okay?

01:44.150 --> 01:44.870
I'm fine.

01:45.430 --> 01:47.289
I just can't stand seeing Jin cry.

01:52.400 --> 01:53.920
Why did it have to be Chuan?

01:55.479 --> 01:56.150
What?

01:56.560 --> 01:58.560
So many people went on that mission,

01:58.640 --> 02:00.040
but only he died.

02:00.790 --> 02:02.640
I don't know what kind of grudge
they could've had against him—

02:02.640 --> 02:04.090
they stabbed him a dozen times

02:04.090 --> 02:05.890
and finished him off with a shot.

02:07.840 --> 02:09.100
Drug dealers like that

02:09.400 --> 02:10.600
will stop at nothing.

02:12.010 --> 02:13.400
But Chuan died.

02:15.310 --> 02:16.310
I was injured too.

02:21.110 --> 02:22.570
But you made it back alive.

02:25.800 --> 02:27.460
What do you mean, Jiang Cheng?

02:27.800 --> 02:29.400
What the hell are you saying?

02:29.470 --> 02:31.280
Would you only be satisfied
if I died too, huh?

02:31.280 --> 02:33.400
Chuan was your brother, but I'm not?

02:33.520 --> 02:34.630
One SWAT officer wasn't enough for you?

02:34.630 --> 02:36.430
You need another body before you're happy?

02:36.430 --> 02:37.800
What the hell is wrong with you, Zhan Wei?

02:37.800 --> 02:38.400
Is that what I meant?

02:38.400 --> 02:39.660
Then what did you mean?

02:40.150 --> 02:40.800
What's going on?

02:40.800 --> 02:42.240
Why are you guys fighting?

02:42.240 --> 02:42.970
Jiang Cheng,

02:43.310 --> 02:45.240
everyone's devastated
about our brother's death.

02:45.240 --> 02:47.100
Don't think you're the only one
entitled to act out.

02:47.100 --> 02:49.230
Who's "acting out"? Say that clearly!

02:49.470 --> 02:51.840
You went on the mission together
that day, right?

02:51.840 --> 02:53.280
You don't even know how he died,

02:53.280 --> 02:54.520
and you still had the nerve to come back?

02:54.520 --> 02:55.800
Why didn't you chase them?

02:55.800 --> 02:57.079
I'm telling you—
if I had been there that day,

02:57.079 --> 02:58.680
I would never have let anyone get away.

02:58.680 --> 03:00.400
Yeah, yeah, you're the most capable!

03:00.400 --> 03:02.210
From now on, you can be
the eldest brother! Count me out!

03:02.210 --> 03:03.590
I don't deserve to be your brother!

03:03.590 --> 03:04.910
Cheng didn't mean that, Wei!

03:04.910 --> 03:06.570
That's exactly what he meant!

03:08.000 --> 03:10.600
You just wished
I were the one who died that day.

03:10.800 --> 03:12.520
Chuan came back, and I died there;

03:12.520 --> 03:14.280
then you'd be satisfied, huh?

03:14.470 --> 03:15.570
What are you doing, Jiang Cheng?

03:15.570 --> 03:16.520
Can you talk like a normal person?

03:16.520 --> 03:17.280
Can you?

03:17.310 --> 03:18.170
Stop fighting!

03:23.680 --> 03:24.590
Wei, Wei!

03:24.590 --> 03:25.450
Don't touch me!

03:25.910 --> 03:26.590
Jin!

03:28.240 --> 03:29.120
Wei!

03:29.890 --> 03:38.700
[Tomb of Martyr Zhou Chuan]

03:31.720 --> 03:32.770
You know what?

03:33.540 --> 03:34.920
Jiang Cheng asked me,

03:35.540 --> 03:38.070
"You and Chuan
went on that mission together.

03:38.520 --> 03:41.110
How come he died and you came back alive?"

03:42.150 --> 03:43.520
He meant nothing by it,

03:44.030 --> 03:45.870
but it scared the hell out of me.

03:45.960 --> 03:47.630
I was sweating all over.

03:58.750 --> 04:00.120
That was a warning.

04:01.000 --> 04:02.460
I have to stop seeing them.

04:03.800 --> 04:05.960
Staying away is the safest thing to do.

04:07.750 --> 04:09.080
Jiang Cheng is like you—

04:09.150 --> 04:11.430
he has to get to the bottom of everything.

04:12.560 --> 04:14.190
I've learned my lesson.

04:15.120 --> 04:17.850
I won't give you anything
to use against me again.

05:36.710 --> 05:42.430
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

05:42.750 --> 05:45.070
[Episode 25]

05:46.680 --> 05:47.830
Zhao Ping?

05:51.070 --> 05:52.130
Never heard of him.

05:57.710 --> 05:59.370
He knew my brother, actually.

06:00.630 --> 06:02.560
Your brother was the top sniper.

06:02.940 --> 06:05.140
It's not surprising if anyone knew him.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.070
True.

06:09.600 --> 06:10.830
During the 8/17 Case,

06:11.630 --> 06:12.560
he was there too.

06:14.190 --> 06:15.520
Then I must have met him,

06:15.680 --> 06:17.480
but the name doesn't ring a bell.

06:17.480 --> 06:19.410
A lot of people were there that day.

06:19.560 --> 06:21.240
Four squadrons sent people.

06:21.240 --> 06:22.310
And everyone wore headgear.

06:22.310 --> 06:23.360
Even if I saw him,

06:23.390 --> 06:25.990
I probably couldn't match
his face to his name.

06:26.190 --> 06:27.000
What?

06:27.040 --> 06:28.430
Want me to look him up for you?

06:28.430 --> 06:29.120
No need.

06:29.950 --> 06:30.800
He's dead.

06:31.070 --> 06:31.950
Dead?

06:32.270 --> 06:32.870
Suicide.

06:38.380 --> 06:38.909
Alright,

06:39.000 --> 06:39.800
I'm full.

06:40.970 --> 06:42.010
What's the rush?

06:42.100 --> 06:43.560
Finish this before you go.

06:43.800 --> 06:44.530
I'll head back first.

06:44.530 --> 06:46.130
You should go back early too.

06:46.250 --> 06:47.920
Your wife is recovering from childbirth.

06:47.920 --> 06:49.310
You should take good care of her.

06:49.310 --> 06:50.820
We have a confinement nanny.

06:50.820 --> 06:51.460
It's fine.

06:51.670 --> 06:52.750
She just had a baby.

06:52.900 --> 06:54.140
You need to pay more attention to her.

06:54.140 --> 06:56.670
Otherwise, she might develop
postpartum depression.

06:56.670 --> 06:57.310
Got it.

06:57.870 --> 06:58.930
I'll get going then, Wei.

06:58.930 --> 06:59.520
Okay.

06:59.580 --> 07:00.580
See you at my baby's one-month party
the day after tomorrow.

07:00.580 --> 07:01.140
Okay.

07:15.230 --> 07:16.580
Zhao Ping is his friend,

07:16.820 --> 07:19.080
but he seems very resistant to Zhao Ping.

07:19.190 --> 07:19.990
You're right.

07:20.190 --> 07:21.430
Their physical distance is close—

07:21.430 --> 07:23.380
the kind of distance
you'd see between acquaintances

07:23.380 --> 07:24.070
or friends.

07:24.140 --> 07:25.340
Do you know Zhao Ping?

07:26.260 --> 07:27.320
Never heard of him.

07:28.830 --> 07:30.630
His left foot is angled outward,

07:31.500 --> 07:32.670
and he's in a defensive stance.

07:32.670 --> 07:34.730
He's looking for an opening to leave.

07:39.020 --> 07:40.190
You scared the hell out of me.

07:40.190 --> 07:41.260
Did I scare you?

07:41.260 --> 07:42.110
Wei.

07:42.990 --> 07:43.990
Take these back.

07:44.260 --> 07:45.500
If Director Wang can eat them,

07:45.500 --> 07:46.350
give them to him.

07:46.350 --> 07:47.060
If not,

07:47.090 --> 07:48.140
keep them for yourself.

07:48.140 --> 07:48.550
Here.

07:48.550 --> 07:49.140
Okay.

08:00.900 --> 08:01.580
Are you crazy?

08:01.580 --> 08:03.040
Watch where you're going!

08:05.940 --> 08:07.230
You're on a road.

08:08.020 --> 08:09.150
You got a death wish?

08:10.750 --> 08:12.350
Good thing you're here, Wei.

08:12.840 --> 08:14.100
What's wrong with you?

08:14.110 --> 08:15.460
You're completely out of it.

08:15.460 --> 08:16.590
Let me walk you back.

08:17.110 --> 08:17.750
No need.

08:17.900 --> 08:19.160
I can go back by myself.

08:19.430 --> 08:20.480
Walk slowly.

08:20.550 --> 08:21.460
Look both ways.

08:22.900 --> 08:24.260
I'm not a kid anymore.

08:30.820 --> 08:31.580
Let me.

08:35.299 --> 08:36.150
Be careful now.

08:36.150 --> 08:36.820
Okay.

08:36.980 --> 08:38.510
Go ahead. I'll watch you go.

08:45.510 --> 08:47.240
Be careful! Watch out for cars!

09:23.670 --> 09:24.790
It's me.

09:25.580 --> 09:27.740
They're starting to suspect me.

09:28.510 --> 09:30.100
This is all your fault!

09:30.250 --> 09:34.980
[Yongchuan Police Station]

09:35.620 --> 09:37.310
Mom, you don't need to be this nervous.

09:37.310 --> 09:38.390
Just a reminder.

09:39.550 --> 09:40.670
Just stay safe

09:40.740 --> 09:42.940
and try not to go to remote places, okay?

09:44.310 --> 09:45.150
I know.

09:46.670 --> 09:47.340
Bye.

10:19.700 --> 10:20.670
You finished?

10:25.740 --> 10:26.670
How did it go?

10:27.580 --> 10:28.910
Did he tell everything?

10:31.190 --> 10:32.070
It was him.

10:34.910 --> 10:36.220
He's seen Qi Yan?

10:40.820 --> 10:42.220
And there's a middleman.

10:42.700 --> 10:43.960
We're looking into it,

10:44.740 --> 10:46.470
but we don't have enough leads.

10:47.070 --> 10:48.930
It won't be easy to track him down.

10:56.980 --> 10:58.980
If he'd really wanted to kill Prof,

10:59.620 --> 11:01.270
he wouldn't have done it

11:01.550 --> 11:03.100
at the Provincial Bureau's dorms.

11:03.100 --> 11:04.220
So brazenly...

11:05.030 --> 11:06.430
It's more like a warning.

11:07.840 --> 11:09.620
Give your dad and Mrs. Fang a call

11:09.620 --> 11:11.410
and tell them to be careful.

11:15.700 --> 11:16.900
Then wait for me here.

11:27.310 --> 11:28.030
These...

11:28.360 --> 11:29.420
Wei gave them to me.

11:39.120 --> 11:40.270
Dad, it's me.

11:41.910 --> 11:43.310
How have you been lately?

11:50.100 --> 11:52.030
Knowing the criminal's
personality weaknesses

11:52.030 --> 11:53.830
means knowing how to enrage him.

11:53.860 --> 11:55.190
I just threw out bait,

11:55.790 --> 11:56.790
and he took it.

11:56.980 --> 11:57.790
What bait?

12:00.370 --> 12:01.020
Me.

13:10.310 --> 13:11.310
Hansheng.

13:16.520 --> 13:17.520
I love you.

13:22.900 --> 13:25.030
[Wei, are you free tomorrow?]

13:25.120 --> 13:28.040
[Yeah, what do you have in mind?]

13:51.720 --> 13:52.650
I'm heading out.

13:53.120 --> 13:53.760
Now?

13:55.370 --> 13:56.740
What time are you meeting Wei?

13:56.740 --> 13:58.000
We're meeting at noon.

13:58.430 --> 14:00.310
But I want to go pick up a gift first

14:00.470 --> 14:01.670
for my little nephew.

14:02.100 --> 14:04.070
Maybe a bracelet or a necklace.

14:04.150 --> 14:05.410
I haven't decided yet.

14:06.290 --> 14:08.030
Are you sure you don't want me to come?

14:08.030 --> 14:08.670
It's okay.

14:10.040 --> 14:11.270
I'll just pop over to his place

14:11.270 --> 14:12.130
to see the baby.

14:12.450 --> 14:13.650
You go visit Mr. Wang.

14:16.430 --> 14:17.850
Remember to have breakfast.

14:17.850 --> 14:18.280
Okay.

14:18.840 --> 14:19.700
Have you eaten?

14:22.290 --> 14:23.220
I'm heading out.

14:30.520 --> 14:31.920
It's getting cold today.

14:32.100 --> 14:33.230
Can I wear your coat?

14:33.400 --> 14:34.000
Of course.

14:40.110 --> 14:40.570
Come on.

15:04.550 --> 15:05.270
I'm off.

15:06.340 --> 15:07.600
Take care of yourself.

15:13.890 --> 15:14.820
Remember to eat.

15:18.340 --> 15:18.850
Bye.

16:06.030 --> 16:06.620
These...

16:06.940 --> 16:08.000
Wei gave them to me.

16:08.430 --> 16:11.000
Wei works in the Information Department
at the Provincial Bureau.

16:11.000 --> 16:11.930
Nice to meet you.

16:12.030 --> 16:12.760
I'm Zhan Wei.

16:14.040 --> 16:15.620
Who's that person next to him?

16:15.620 --> 16:16.550
Hard to make out.

16:17.170 --> 16:17.890
Too blurry.

16:18.840 --> 16:20.500
We'll have to verify it again.

16:34.030 --> 16:35.030
Professor Jiang.

16:38.790 --> 16:39.430
Wei.

16:41.200 --> 16:41.840
Jin.

16:43.000 --> 16:44.030
For my nephew.

16:44.060 --> 16:45.230
You just bought it, didn't you?

16:45.230 --> 16:47.090
No wonder you wanted to meet here.

16:47.320 --> 16:47.910
Thanks.

16:50.960 --> 16:51.760
What's wrong?

16:52.030 --> 16:54.760
That's obviously
your husband's coat, isn't it?

16:54.790 --> 16:55.910
If your brother were here,

16:55.910 --> 16:58.710
he'd say
you're dressing inappropriately again.

16:59.840 --> 17:00.770
Let's go. Get in.

17:12.660 --> 17:14.130
Why the sudden decision to leave today?

17:14.130 --> 17:15.520
Can't you stay one more day?

17:15.520 --> 17:17.069
Besides, today is Saturday.

17:17.069 --> 17:17.859
There's a mission at the station.

17:17.859 --> 17:19.520
They need me back by tomorrow.

17:20.250 --> 17:22.530
Seems our Jin is the backbone of the team.

17:22.560 --> 17:23.579
They can't manage without you.

17:23.579 --> 17:25.980
It's mostly because we're short-staffed.

17:33.140 --> 17:34.870
Slow down. Don't get too close.

17:43.630 --> 17:44.470
Qian,

17:44.490 --> 17:45.520
maintain a safe distance.

17:45.520 --> 17:45.990
Okay,

17:46.250 --> 17:46.980
understood.

17:59.310 --> 18:00.310
Is your place far?

18:00.880 --> 18:02.010
It's a bit of a drive.

18:02.030 --> 18:03.960
Why else would I come to pick you up?

18:04.620 --> 18:06.480
You can't make it
to my baby's one-month party,

18:06.480 --> 18:08.280
so you're making a special trip.

18:08.790 --> 18:10.310
You're a pretty good aunt.

18:11.860 --> 18:13.520
Then tell me, how much should I

18:13.930 --> 18:15.750
put in the red envelope as his aunt?

18:15.750 --> 18:17.100
We don't accept money.

18:17.130 --> 18:18.590
You don't need to give one.

18:18.950 --> 18:19.750
Why so formal?

18:19.750 --> 18:21.460
I've already withdrawn the cash.

18:21.460 --> 18:22.940
We're not allowed to accept any now.

18:22.940 --> 18:24.700
It might look like bribery.

18:25.380 --> 18:26.420
Your presence is enough.

18:26.420 --> 18:28.480
Besides, you already brought a gift.

18:28.600 --> 18:31.380
Actually, we weren't supposed to
accept gifts either.

18:31.380 --> 18:32.910
So strict even with family?

18:33.360 --> 18:34.320
We have to be.

18:34.990 --> 18:36.870
It's a matter of principle.

18:37.550 --> 18:38.660
And you're

18:39.100 --> 18:41.430
still hosting the party at Nanshan Manor?

18:41.470 --> 18:43.800
Just the name sounds pretty extravagant.

18:44.030 --> 18:46.430
Aren't you afraid of
what people might say?

18:46.900 --> 18:48.300
That place is beautiful.

18:48.700 --> 18:49.750
My wife likes it.

18:53.750 --> 18:55.190
After we're done at my place,

18:55.190 --> 18:57.760
I'll take you over to have a look.
How about that?

18:57.760 --> 18:59.560
What time is your train tonight?

19:07.100 --> 19:07.550
Jin?

19:11.140 --> 19:12.070
Half past eight.

19:13.470 --> 19:15.000
Then we have plenty of time.

19:20.900 --> 19:21.900
Professor Jiang,

19:22.180 --> 19:23.230
has Bai Yang arrived?

19:23.230 --> 19:23.830
He's here.

19:24.380 --> 19:24.980
Chief Tan,

19:25.470 --> 19:26.670
what's going on here?

19:26.740 --> 19:27.740
Where is Zhou Jin?

19:28.350 --> 19:29.150
Zhou Jin is...

19:29.910 --> 19:32.170
currently in the middle of an operation.

19:32.460 --> 19:33.720
Just hear me out first.

19:34.040 --> 19:35.900
Zhou Jin reported to me last night

19:36.510 --> 19:37.370
that she's made

19:37.660 --> 19:39.140
a major discovery in Jingzhou.

19:39.140 --> 19:39.950
However,

19:40.230 --> 19:41.790
she hasn't found any solid evidence yet.

19:41.790 --> 19:43.100
So she wants to use

19:43.310 --> 19:44.980
her personal friendship with the suspect

19:44.980 --> 19:46.380
to gather information

19:46.460 --> 19:47.940
and confirm

19:48.030 --> 19:49.030
whether her initial deduction

19:49.030 --> 19:49.820
is correct.

19:50.420 --> 19:51.310
This suspect

19:51.550 --> 19:53.420
is Zhan Wei from the Provincial Bureau's
Information Department?

19:53.420 --> 19:54.050
Yes.

19:54.180 --> 19:55.100
Zhou Jin suspects that he's

19:55.100 --> 19:56.790
connected to her brother's death.

19:56.790 --> 19:57.650
And may even be,

19:58.420 --> 19:59.580
just like Zhao Ping,

20:00.240 --> 20:01.480
one of Qi Yan's men.

20:02.790 --> 20:03.990
Zhan Wei and Zhao Ping

20:04.230 --> 20:06.090
joined SWAT around the same time,

20:06.420 --> 20:07.940
so they must know each other.

20:07.940 --> 20:10.280
But Zhan Wei has been
adamantly denying it,

20:10.280 --> 20:12.280
which makes him highly suspicious.

20:12.990 --> 20:13.820
Listen,

20:14.130 --> 20:15.420
I went to the SWAT team

20:15.510 --> 20:17.130
and checked the deployment roster

20:17.130 --> 20:18.620
for the 8/17 Case.

20:18.790 --> 20:20.050
There were 40 in total.

20:20.270 --> 20:20.950
Zhou Chuan,

20:21.560 --> 20:22.170
Zhan Wei,

20:22.800 --> 20:23.530
and Zhao Ping

20:23.900 --> 20:25.030
were all on the list.

20:25.510 --> 20:26.310
To be honest,

20:26.620 --> 20:28.510
if it weren't for what Zhao Ping said

20:28.510 --> 20:29.990
before he jumped off the building,

20:29.990 --> 20:31.950
no one would've thought to look into this.

20:31.950 --> 20:33.750
How is Zhou Jin going to
get information out of him?

20:33.750 --> 20:35.140
If Zhan Wei really works for Qi Yan,

20:35.140 --> 20:36.750
she's in great danger right now!

20:36.750 --> 20:37.350
Chief Tan,

20:37.480 --> 20:39.130
how far has this mission progressed?

20:39.130 --> 20:40.750
Can we suspend it immediately?

20:40.750 --> 20:41.950
They've already met.

20:47.960 --> 20:48.960
Professor Jiang.

20:51.820 --> 20:52.270
Yes.

20:52.690 --> 20:53.890
Don't panic yet.

20:54.170 --> 20:55.910
Zhou Jin was afraid that if you knew,

20:55.910 --> 20:56.770
you would worry

20:56.800 --> 20:58.230
and refuse to let her go through with it.

20:58.230 --> 20:59.540
So before the operation,

20:59.540 --> 21:01.200
she kept some things from you.

21:02.340 --> 21:02.910
But

21:02.950 --> 21:04.270
objectively speaking,

21:04.270 --> 21:05.820
Qi Yan has been off the grid

21:06.230 --> 21:07.560
for quite some time now.

21:07.690 --> 21:09.370
We need a breakthrough.

21:10.030 --> 21:10.830
I understand.

21:11.750 --> 21:12.270
Also,

21:12.450 --> 21:13.520
Zhou Jin asked me

21:13.580 --> 21:14.840
to tell you something.

21:16.340 --> 21:16.950
What is it?

21:17.570 --> 21:18.500
She said only you

21:19.540 --> 21:20.780
can always find her.

21:24.400 --> 21:25.200
I understand.

21:26.890 --> 21:28.290
I'll cooperate with her.

21:28.340 --> 21:28.860
Good.

21:28.990 --> 21:30.360
I sent Bai Yang

21:30.490 --> 21:32.350
to provide you with technical support.

21:32.350 --> 21:33.120
At the scene,

21:33.200 --> 21:34.540
Wan has got things covered.

21:34.540 --> 21:35.430
In short,

21:35.450 --> 21:37.610
everything is under control.

21:37.700 --> 21:38.800
You don't need to worry too much.

21:38.800 --> 21:39.790
All we need to do

21:39.830 --> 21:42.160
is keep close tabs on Zhou Jin's progress.

21:42.660 --> 21:43.140
Also,

21:43.480 --> 21:45.410
I'm on my way to Jingzhou right now.

21:46.750 --> 21:47.270
Okay.

22:00.340 --> 22:01.340
Professor Jiang,

22:01.480 --> 22:03.140
this is Mr. Wan and the others.

22:06.820 --> 22:07.760
Zhou Jin is here.

22:32.650 --> 22:34.510
Is it completely jammed up ahead?

22:36.490 --> 22:38.620
We've hit the usual traffic jam again.

22:40.200 --> 22:42.400
This is the way out of the city, isn't it?

22:44.840 --> 22:46.640
Taking the outer ring is faster.

22:46.640 --> 22:47.690
It's the weekend.

22:47.710 --> 22:49.570
Traffic in the city is even worse.

22:57.470 --> 22:58.730
Don't bother looking.

22:59.380 --> 23:00.310
There's

23:01.340 --> 23:02.630
no signal in my car.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.680
Where exactly are you taking me?

23:15.290 --> 23:17.150
We don't have solid evidence yet,

23:17.790 --> 23:19.280
but we need to ask Chief Liang

23:19.280 --> 23:21.140
to keep some officers on standby.

23:21.470 --> 23:22.820
We might need them very soon.

23:22.820 --> 23:23.180
Okay.

23:23.420 --> 23:24.350
I'll contact him right away.

23:24.350 --> 23:24.820
Okay.

23:27.670 --> 23:28.870
Mr. Wan, Mr. Wan,

23:28.890 --> 23:30.090
don't tail them too closely.

23:30.090 --> 23:31.090
If you lose them,

23:31.110 --> 23:33.340
I'll give you their real-time location.

23:33.340 --> 23:34.420
Okay, copy that.

23:34.920 --> 23:36.520
Don't tail them too closely.

23:40.130 --> 23:41.660
Didn't you ask me yesterday

23:42.580 --> 23:43.660
if I knew Zhao Ping?

23:45.030 --> 23:46.290
I remembered it later.

23:46.620 --> 23:47.480
Yes, I knew him.

23:49.340 --> 23:50.200
Were you close?

23:50.580 --> 23:51.420
Sort of.

23:52.310 --> 23:54.110
When he jumped off the building,

23:54.330 --> 23:55.310
you were there?

24:01.440 --> 24:03.030
When Zhao Ping died,

24:03.660 --> 24:05.420
did he say something to you?

24:07.800 --> 24:10.600
You've been suspecting me all along,
haven't you?

24:14.420 --> 24:15.680
Suspected you of what?

24:16.820 --> 24:18.870
No need to keep up the act, Jin.

24:19.620 --> 24:22.510
The fact that you managed to
trace it to me is impressive enough.

24:22.510 --> 24:24.400
But I knew Zhao Ping too well.

24:24.780 --> 24:26.490
That guy was too soft-hearted.

24:26.490 --> 24:27.280
Useless.

24:27.820 --> 24:29.230
I reminded him many times

24:29.250 --> 24:31.090
to find a chance to get rid of you.

24:31.390 --> 24:32.450
But he wouldn't listen.

24:32.450 --> 24:33.750
If he had listened to me earlier,

24:33.750 --> 24:34.900
he'd have already been abroad

24:34.900 --> 24:37.310
with the money, starting a brand-new life.

24:37.310 --> 24:39.910
Why would he have needed to
jump off a building?

24:40.200 --> 24:41.200
So,

24:41.660 --> 24:42.950
those who don't listen

24:43.470 --> 24:45.140
never end up well.

24:46.680 --> 24:47.470
Jin,

24:48.350 --> 24:50.030
didn't I also advise you

24:51.480 --> 24:52.960
not to be so stubborn?

24:53.420 --> 24:54.820
You're a girl.

24:54.850 --> 24:56.500
Just get married properly,

24:56.900 --> 24:58.070
have a child or two,

24:58.070 --> 24:59.620
and live your life in peace—

24:59.650 --> 25:01.050
wouldn't that be better?

25:03.400 --> 25:06.240
But why are you just like

25:06.270 --> 25:07.620
your damn brother?

25:12.550 --> 25:13.680
So it really was you.

25:14.260 --> 25:15.950
He forced me!

25:18.000 --> 25:19.140
Did I make

25:19.140 --> 25:21.230
some unforgivable mistake back then?

25:21.230 --> 25:22.100
No!

25:23.090 --> 25:25.220
You want to know what happened, right?

25:26.050 --> 25:26.900
I'll tell you.

25:27.550 --> 25:30.110
Back then, I was just leading
a routine police response

25:30.110 --> 25:32.470
and ran into some armed thugs brawling.

25:32.540 --> 25:33.890
Someone died,

25:33.910 --> 25:35.420
so the case became serious.

25:35.420 --> 25:36.030
Their boss

25:36.030 --> 25:37.650
wanted to invite me and my superior
to dinner,

25:37.650 --> 25:39.410
hoping to bury the case.

25:40.070 --> 25:42.610
My superior was too principled.
He wouldn't go.

25:42.610 --> 25:43.980
But that screwed me!

25:44.620 --> 25:47.420
My sick mother fell into their hands!

25:47.450 --> 25:49.420
Could I not go to that dinner?

25:50.020 --> 25:51.090
If it were you—

25:51.380 --> 25:52.400
for the sake of your brother—

25:52.400 --> 25:53.730
could you have refused?

25:55.990 --> 25:57.630
They had the pull to smooth things over.

25:57.630 --> 25:59.220
What was I?

25:59.970 --> 26:02.030
Not only did they
leave my mother unharmed,

26:02.030 --> 26:04.510
but they also gave me 200,000
as hush money.

26:05.310 --> 26:07.200
I chose to keep my mouth shut.

26:08.000 --> 26:09.240
200,000.

26:09.750 --> 26:12.710
I didn't make that much in a year.

26:15.030 --> 26:16.270
And for that money,

26:16.790 --> 26:17.990
you became like this?

26:18.860 --> 26:20.340
That's exactly

26:20.990 --> 26:23.780
what your brother said.

26:24.580 --> 26:27.140
That's why I hated Zhou Chuan so much.

26:27.710 --> 26:30.390
Easy for you to say
when it's not your neck on the line.

26:30.390 --> 26:32.580
You always stand on some moral high ground

26:32.580 --> 26:33.860
to judge others.

26:33.860 --> 26:35.530
What about me? What was I supposed to do?

26:35.530 --> 26:36.910
Go head-to-head with them,

26:36.910 --> 26:39.190
risking my job and my life

26:39.220 --> 26:40.460
to turn them in?

26:40.760 --> 26:41.520
Zhou Jin,

26:41.820 --> 26:43.820
I was just a rookie cop at the time!

26:43.840 --> 26:45.270
I chose to take the money
and keep my mouth shut!

26:45.270 --> 26:47.330
Is that really so hard to understand?

26:47.860 --> 26:51.180
[2012]

26:55.070 --> 26:56.950
So there's no room for discussion, huh?

26:56.950 --> 26:57.750
About what?

27:02.340 --> 27:03.820
I'll vouch for you

27:04.340 --> 27:05.910
and introduce you to them.

27:06.790 --> 27:07.820
I'll split

27:08.380 --> 27:09.510
that money with you.

27:12.950 --> 27:13.550
Wei,

27:14.470 --> 27:15.550
turn yourself in.

27:17.240 --> 27:17.990
Chuan,

27:18.930 --> 27:20.450
if you were in my shoes,

27:20.470 --> 27:22.180
you'd understand
that so much of what I've done

27:22.180 --> 27:23.860
was out of desperation!

27:23.920 --> 27:25.070
I can turn myself in.

27:25.070 --> 27:26.380
I can give up my job and even my life.

27:26.380 --> 27:27.860
But what about my family?

27:28.070 --> 27:29.070
Just because you refused

27:29.070 --> 27:30.750
to side with them,

27:30.790 --> 27:32.310
they came after your parents

27:32.310 --> 27:33.270
and your girlfriend—

27:33.270 --> 27:34.270
what would you do?

27:34.270 --> 27:35.550
If they dared lay a finger on my family,

27:35.550 --> 27:37.340
I'd arrest every last one of them!

27:37.340 --> 27:38.900
I'd have the courage
to go down fighting with them!

27:38.900 --> 27:39.580
Do you?

27:39.860 --> 27:40.990
Being a police officer,

27:40.990 --> 27:42.210
you need to have some real grit!

27:42.210 --> 27:42.840
Zhan Wei,

27:42.860 --> 27:43.820
don't forget

27:44.030 --> 27:45.550
you are a police officer!

28:05.620 --> 28:07.350
When you first joined the unit,

28:08.470 --> 28:10.600
there was a young officer in your squad

28:10.720 --> 28:13.200
who accidentally threw a grenade
into the trench.

28:13.200 --> 28:14.470
Without even thinking,

28:14.470 --> 28:16.270
you picked it up and threw it out.

28:16.710 --> 28:18.770
Then you threw yourself over the kid,

28:19.030 --> 28:20.950
shielding him with your own body.

28:21.170 --> 28:22.230
You saved his life.

28:22.580 --> 28:24.040
That's who you really are.

28:24.580 --> 28:25.270
I know

28:26.380 --> 28:29.440
you've worked harder than anyone else
all these years.

28:29.820 --> 28:31.270
You've endured a lot of hardship

28:31.270 --> 28:32.870
to get to where you are today.

28:36.700 --> 28:39.160
But you lost sight of
what you once stood for.

28:40.470 --> 28:42.420
I don't want those people
to ruin the Zhan Wei

28:42.420 --> 28:45.480
who once threw himself into harm's way
to save someone.

28:45.990 --> 28:47.270
I don't want those people

28:47.270 --> 28:48.820
to ruin my brother.

28:56.070 --> 28:56.790
Wei.

28:59.070 --> 29:00.270
There are some things

29:00.890 --> 29:02.950
you need to think through carefully.

29:05.450 --> 29:07.210
I hope the next time I see you,

29:08.620 --> 29:10.480
it'll be in the captain's office.

29:17.710 --> 29:18.380
Chuan.

29:43.820 --> 29:45.420
Jin's birthday is coming up.

29:47.700 --> 29:49.830
This is the present I prepared for her.

29:52.270 --> 29:53.000
Don't worry.

29:53.820 --> 29:55.620
I paid for it out of my own pocket.

29:56.710 --> 29:58.370
No matter what you think of me,

29:58.510 --> 29:59.470
you'll

30:00.790 --> 30:02.920
always be the ones I hold closest.

30:07.950 --> 30:09.280
As for taking the money,

30:09.480 --> 30:11.010
I'll come clean to the unit.

30:11.820 --> 30:12.470
Chuan,

30:13.180 --> 30:14.710
just give me a few more days.

30:16.580 --> 30:18.240
I want to go back to my hometown

30:19.370 --> 30:20.280
to see my mom.

30:27.770 --> 30:28.450
I know.

30:30.510 --> 30:32.370
I know it's hard to take this step.

30:35.140 --> 30:36.230
But you have to

30:37.030 --> 30:37.990
get through it.

30:40.750 --> 30:41.750
Don't let me down.

30:45.230 --> 30:47.310
When we come back
from the mission on the 17th,

30:47.310 --> 30:49.170
let's have a good drink together.

30:50.580 --> 30:51.790
You said it.

30:52.580 --> 30:53.340
It's a deal.

30:55.660 --> 30:56.520
A deal's a deal.

31:17.180 --> 31:17.820
It's me.

31:19.890 --> 31:22.450
I agree to all your previous demands.

31:24.180 --> 31:29.900
[August 17, 2012]

31:55.980 --> 31:56.550
Move in!

32:04.100 --> 32:04.790
Freeze!

32:06.340 --> 32:07.000
Don't move!

32:11.710 --> 32:12.710
Police!

32:13.230 --> 32:13.790
Freeze!

32:15.950 --> 32:17.070
Don't move!

32:20.580 --> 32:21.510
Police!

32:22.030 --> 32:22.660
Freeze!

32:25.330 --> 32:26.030
Freeze!

32:28.230 --> 32:29.020
No... Don't...

32:29.020 --> 32:29.420
Don't... Don't...

32:29.420 --> 32:29.750
Don't move!

32:29.750 --> 32:30.100
Please!

32:30.100 --> 32:31.740
It's my first time! I don't know anything!

32:31.740 --> 32:32.420
Zhao Ning?

32:32.580 --> 32:33.340
Is there anyone else here?

32:33.340 --> 32:34.810
Bring everyone you've caught over
to the vehicles!

32:34.810 --> 32:35.330
Sir,

32:35.380 --> 32:36.550
armed drug dealers spotted

32:36.550 --> 32:37.230
in the northwest corner!

32:37.230 --> 32:38.360
Requesting backup!

32:38.810 --> 32:40.660
What are you doing? You scared me!

32:40.660 --> 32:42.180
Can you do me a favor?

32:42.430 --> 32:43.060
What is it?

32:43.090 --> 32:43.660
Tell me.

32:43.820 --> 32:45.340
The guy with the beard in the car

32:45.340 --> 32:46.470
is my cousin.

32:47.440 --> 32:49.080
Could you put in a word with Captain Zhou

32:49.080 --> 32:49.800
for me?

32:50.140 --> 32:51.140
He's still a kid,

32:51.140 --> 32:52.340
just graduated from college.

32:52.340 --> 32:53.180
If he gets caught,

32:53.180 --> 32:54.340
his life is ruined.

32:54.340 --> 32:55.740
Are you crazy, Zhao Ping?

32:55.770 --> 32:56.660
You know

32:56.660 --> 32:57.990
what Zhou Chuan is like!

32:58.790 --> 33:00.020
I can't help you with this.

33:00.020 --> 33:00.310
Yes.

33:00.310 --> 33:02.240
I-I know what Captain Zhou is like.

33:02.450 --> 33:04.270
But he's the only son in his family!

33:04.270 --> 33:06.300
His parents are counting on him!

33:06.510 --> 33:07.630
If he goes to prison,

33:07.630 --> 33:08.630
it's really over—

33:08.660 --> 33:09.950
the whole family will be destroyed!

33:09.950 --> 33:11.790
So could you please help me talk to...

33:11.790 --> 33:12.860
Unless...

33:15.270 --> 33:16.870
you can draw Zhou Chuan away—

33:17.320 --> 33:18.720
the further, the better.

33:19.030 --> 33:20.760
I'll find a chance to let him go.

33:22.560 --> 33:23.030
Okay.

33:23.660 --> 33:24.340
Okay.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.080
Remember.

33:27.180 --> 33:29.140
Don't alert anyone.

33:30.550 --> 33:31.280
Understood.

33:37.710 --> 33:38.510
Captain Zhou!

33:38.860 --> 33:39.860
I noticed a place.

33:40.070 --> 33:41.100
Looks very suspicious.

33:41.100 --> 33:42.020
Do you want to go and take a look?

33:42.020 --> 33:42.750
Where is it?

33:42.750 --> 33:43.380
I'll take you there.

33:43.380 --> 33:43.910
Let's go.

33:56.500 --> 33:57.430
Is it here?

33:58.580 --> 33:58.990
It...

33:59.270 --> 34:00.380
it should be here.

34:02.950 --> 34:04.420
They were right here just now.

34:04.420 --> 34:05.150
Are you sure?

34:06.940 --> 34:08.020
Maybe it's ahead.

34:09.139 --> 34:10.330
If you really found something,

34:10.330 --> 34:11.929
you'll make a contribution.

34:25.070 --> 34:26.330
There's nothing here.

34:27.350 --> 34:28.150
Captain Zhou.

34:28.179 --> 34:28.909
Zhao Ping,

34:29.139 --> 34:30.940
do you have something to tell me?

34:31.139 --> 34:31.940
Captain Zhou.

34:32.100 --> 34:33.060
Actually, I...

34:57.150 --> 34:58.360
You hurt me.

35:17.370 --> 35:18.700
Your name is Zhou Chuan?

35:20.030 --> 35:20.990
Who are you?

35:21.900 --> 35:23.500
I have no grudge against you.

35:23.540 --> 35:24.870
I don't want to kill you.

35:25.430 --> 35:26.660
It's your brother

35:27.040 --> 35:28.100
who wants you dead.

35:29.470 --> 35:30.350
Sorry.

35:41.050 --> 35:41.740
Thank you.

35:47.630 --> 35:48.510
Zhan Wei,

35:49.150 --> 35:50.810
come out and collect the body!

36:04.160 --> 36:06.340
Do you know how I felt

36:06.370 --> 36:08.040
when Zhou Chuan died?

36:09.510 --> 36:11.510
The whole world went quiet,

36:12.400 --> 36:14.230
and my heart was at peace.

36:16.870 --> 36:17.660
Zhou Jin,

36:18.620 --> 36:20.220
don't be so naive.

36:20.880 --> 36:23.230
Let me tell you two final truths.

36:24.350 --> 36:25.220
First,

36:25.390 --> 36:27.260
those who can read the situation

36:27.470 --> 36:29.300
will never lose.

36:29.700 --> 36:31.100
Actually, just like you,

36:31.620 --> 36:33.100
I really hate Qi Yan.

36:33.470 --> 36:35.140
That man is a lunatic.

36:35.510 --> 36:37.700
That's why I kept encouraging you
to investigate,

36:37.700 --> 36:39.700
hoping you'd bring him down

36:39.700 --> 36:40.910
for me.

36:41.740 --> 36:42.780
I'd been

36:42.810 --> 36:44.470
looking into the two undercovers

36:44.470 --> 36:46.190
Yao Weihai planted
around Qi Yan five years ago.

36:46.190 --> 36:47.550
One was Meng Junfeng.

36:47.570 --> 36:49.770
Before I could find out about the other,

36:49.920 --> 36:51.950
Yao Weihai discovered
that the undercover files had been leaked

36:51.950 --> 36:54.390
and deleted everything.

36:55.030 --> 36:58.070
Yet Meng Junfeng wasn't exposed
until five years later.

36:58.070 --> 36:59.510
Do you know why?

37:00.260 --> 37:02.090
Because I protected him.

37:02.990 --> 37:06.700
It would've been ideal if the task force
could've taken down Qi Yan.

37:06.700 --> 37:08.100
But later, I heard

37:09.990 --> 37:11.780
that both Meng Junfeng and Yao Weihai

37:11.780 --> 37:13.950
were outwitted and killed by Qi Yan.

37:14.280 --> 37:15.800
Qi Yan was the winner.

37:15.830 --> 37:18.060
So I stand on the winner's side.

37:18.470 --> 37:20.870
That's what it means
to read the situation.

37:21.430 --> 37:22.830
And another truth—

37:23.300 --> 37:25.260
if you want to win to the very end,

37:25.700 --> 37:28.660
you have to be willing to risk it all.

37:34.580 --> 37:35.550
Jin...

37:37.840 --> 37:40.590
you shouldn't have gotten into my car.

38:04.430 --> 38:05.160
Hansheng...

38:21.660 --> 38:22.910
We finally meet.

38:25.700 --> 38:26.660
Officer Zhou.

38:27.890 --> 38:28.560
Bai Yang,

38:28.890 --> 38:29.830
what's going on ahead?

38:29.830 --> 38:30.830
We're stuck here.

38:32.660 --> 38:34.740
Looks like there's been a traffic accident
up ahead.

38:34.740 --> 38:36.270
I need to check the details.

38:36.620 --> 38:38.420
What about Zhou Jin and Zhan Wei?

38:40.000 --> 38:41.260
They're still moving.

38:41.290 --> 38:42.220
Okay. Copy that.

38:42.870 --> 38:43.550
It's Qi Yan.

38:44.020 --> 38:45.150
Qi Yan took the bait.

38:46.180 --> 38:48.550
For people like me
in the restaurant industry,

38:48.550 --> 38:49.220
we just

38:49.330 --> 38:50.670
can't stand messy tables.

38:50.670 --> 38:52.130
Drives me crazy, you know?

38:52.710 --> 38:54.370
Did Jin reply to your message?

38:57.350 --> 38:57.830
No.

38:59.100 --> 39:00.300
That's fine, I guess.

39:00.350 --> 39:01.070
We don't

39:01.070 --> 39:02.470
all have to give the same amount, right?

39:02.470 --> 39:04.000
As long as ours are the same.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.510
How could she go three hours

39:05.510 --> 39:06.910
without replying to you?

39:07.140 --> 39:07.950
Busy.

39:11.260 --> 39:12.830
You look restless.

39:12.940 --> 39:14.600
Do you need her for something?

39:14.870 --> 39:16.150
Didn't Jin go to Jingzhou

39:16.150 --> 39:17.280
to attend the party?

39:22.300 --> 39:23.180
Stop smoking.

39:23.810 --> 39:25.470
Start by not smoking indoors.

39:27.610 --> 39:28.220
How about this:

39:28.220 --> 39:29.350
give Jin a call.

39:30.690 --> 39:32.320
Call her and see if she picks up.

39:32.320 --> 39:32.920
Hurry.

39:41.950 --> 39:44.470
Hello. The number you dialed
is powered off.

39:46.550 --> 39:47.480
Her phone's off.

39:49.220 --> 39:50.480
Take me to the station.

39:51.890 --> 39:52.550
What station?

39:52.550 --> 39:53.350
You're not even on the force!

39:53.350 --> 39:54.300
Jin's station!

39:58.350 --> 39:59.610
All units, attention.

39:59.620 --> 40:00.430
The hostage is

40:00.630 --> 40:02.430
Zhou Jin, an investigator
from Haizhou City

40:02.430 --> 40:03.300
Nancheng Branch.

40:03.300 --> 40:04.700
The suspect is Qi Yan,

40:05.100 --> 40:05.910
the prime suspect in the 8/17 Case,

40:05.910 --> 40:06.600
the Huaiguang Case,

40:06.600 --> 40:08.130
and the Jingang Wharf Case.

40:08.140 --> 40:09.260
The suspect is extremely dangerous,

40:09.260 --> 40:10.300
armed with firearms,

40:10.300 --> 40:12.830
and shows clear hostility
toward the police.

40:20.110 --> 40:22.310
There's an intersection
about 500 meters ahead,

40:22.310 --> 40:23.910
heading toward the suburbs.

40:28.530 --> 40:29.210
Umm...

40:29.400 --> 40:30.530
Professor Jiang...

40:31.000 --> 40:33.930
T-There's a speed limit on this road.
How about we...

40:34.320 --> 40:35.520
What's the distance?

40:37.580 --> 40:38.510
2.3 kilometers.

40:47.780 --> 40:48.450
No!

40:49.140 --> 40:50.270
He's toying with us.

40:50.510 --> 40:52.240
He's headed back into the city.

41:00.390 --> 41:01.510
We're almost there.

41:01.510 --> 41:02.740
There's a small side road ahead.

41:02.740 --> 41:04.000
Turn left in 50 meters.

41:05.100 --> 41:07.300
There's an apartment complex
called Desi'en.

41:07.300 --> 41:08.350
Once past the side road,

41:08.350 --> 41:09.610
the traffic clears up.

41:12.640 --> 41:14.040
I've stayed here before.

41:36.390 --> 41:37.700
The tracking signals have now overlapped,

41:37.700 --> 41:38.550
but I can't determine

41:38.550 --> 41:40.430
exactly which room they're in,
Professor Jiang.

41:40.430 --> 41:41.430
Professor Jiang.

41:41.580 --> 41:42.560
Professor Jiang!

41:42.560 --> 41:43.660
They might have guns.

41:43.660 --> 41:44.660
I suggest we...
